TestRigor: A Comprehensive Framework for Automated Software Testing
how it works: give your test description, and it generates test cases, executes them, and reports results.
https://app.testrigor.com/test-suites/wGcnyuhkfessL7P9x/test-cases
TestRigor is an advanced automated software testing framework designed to streamline the testing process. By simply providing a description of the test you want to perform,
 TestRigor generates relevant test cases, executes them, and compiles detailed reports on the results.

 TestRigor is an AI-powered test automation tool that allows QA engineers to create and run tests using plain English commands instead of traditional code.
It focuses on codeless automation using Natural Language Processing (NLP) and Generative AI to reduce maintenance and speed up test creation.

