| ---------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **UI / End-to-End Testing**  | Automates full user workflows across browser and mobile.                  |
| **Functional Testing**       | Validates app features using human-like actions and NLP test steps.       |
| **API Testing**              | Supports REST/SOAP calls and validations directly within same test suite. |
| **Regression Testing**       | Self-healing tests reduce maintenance during frequent UI changes.         |
| **Acceptance Testing (UAT)** | Business teams can write executable test cases in plain English.          |



Where You Can Use It (as QA Automation Engineer)

To quickly automate smoke and regression tests without writing code.

To convert manual test cases into automated ones.

To reduce maintenance of flaky UI tests.

To enable non-technical testers or business users to contribute to automation.


Integrations

Works with Jenkins, GitHub Actions, CircleCI, and other CI/CD tools.

Can integrate with JIRA, TestRail, and Slack for test tracking and reporting.

Supports BrowserStack and Sauce Labs for cross-browser testing.